description: 9-acre view lot on top of the mountain... Stunning territorial views from the top of the world! One of two adjacent parcels can be purchased together or separately. Roads are somewhat primitive; property was surveyed in the 70's or 80's. Water & septic need to be installed & power must be brought to the site. Soil is rocky with silty clay soil on top. No irrigation...
